name: iShares Core Canadian 15+ Year Federal Bond Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to provide income. ETF seeks to provide income by replicating, to the extent possible, the performance of an index that is broadly representative of Government of Canada bonds with remaining maturities of 15 years and greater, net of expenses. The current index for the ETF is the Bloomberg Canada 15+ Year Federal Bond Float Adjusted Index.
